subproject.description:
Outcome 1: 
A functioning regional Women Police Officers Network (WPON) in South East Europe (SEE) promotes and strengthens gender equality in policing in the region and contributes to improved community policing and enhanced public security.

Outcome 2:
Women police officers of South East Europe increase their coordination on issues related to the promotion of gender in policing, education and project consulting.
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: SEEWomenPoliceOfficers Network
